[[File:Enjoy car sharing logo.png|thumb|Logo]] '''Enjoy''' is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[car sharing]] service provided by [[Eni]]. Enjoy is active in [[Milan]], [[Turin]], [[Rome]], [[Florence]] and [[Catania]] with a total of more than 2,000 cars. The system offers exclusively [[Fiat 500 (2007)|Fiat 500]] vehicles with one-way point-to-point rentals charged by the minute. Cars can be rented wherever parked via a smartphone app.<ref>{{cite web|title=Come funziona|url=https://enjoy.eni.com/it/milano/come_funziona|website=enjoy.eni.com|publisher=Eni|accessdate=24 November 2014}}</ref>
