{{italic title}} '''''Frau im Spiegel''''' (English lit. "Woman in the Mirror") is a [[German language|German]] weekly magazine for women based in [[Munich, Germany]].
==History and profile== The magazine first appeared in 1945. It was distributed by the [[Hamburg]]<ref name="Eur2002">{{cite book|title=Western Europe 2003|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=M9QYndAPmuQC&pg=PA294|accessdate=28 February 2016|date=30 November 2002|publisher=Psychology Press|isbn=978-1-85743-152-0|page=294}}</ref> based ''Verlag Ehrlich & Sohn''. The magazine is published weekly by the Funke Women Group GMBH.<ref name="pub">{{cite web|title=Frau im Spiegel|url=http://www.publicitas.com/matrix-media/media-solutions/factsheet/mediadata/frau-im-spiegel/?PARAM1=WD3FL1#.V914PZOLQxc|work=Publicitas|accessdate=17 September 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918031606/http://www.publicitas.com/matrix-media/media-solutions/factsheet/mediadata/frau-im-spiegel/?PARAM1=WD3FL1#.V914PZOLQxc|archivedate=18 September 2016|df=}}</ref> The magazine has its headquarters in Munich.<ref name="pub"/> It is also distributed in the United States by German Language Publications in [[Englewood, NJ]].
Like other German [[Tabloid (newspaper format)|tabloid]] magazines, it reports about European royalty and other celebrities, including gossip and scandals. Other regular topics are health, [[make-up]] tips, fashion, and travel.
According to G+J Electronic Media Sales, the average age of the 88% female readership is age 42.4.<ref>[http://www.gujmedia.de/titel/frau_im_spiegel/profil/index.html?PHPSESSID=1f98723256cae14ae282542d49acf0d3 Frau im Spiegel Profil]{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} {{de icon}}</ref> The [[chief editor]] is Karin Schlautmann.
In the period of 2001-2002 ''Frau im Spiegel'' was one of top 50 women's magazine worldwide with a circulation of 645,000 copies.<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 50 Women’s magazines worldwide (by circulation)|url=http://www.magazine.org.tw/events/school/report/wmt/Top50Womens.pdf|work=Magazines|accessdate=30 March 2015}}</ref> In the third quarter of 2005 the magazine sold 553,051 copies.<ref>[http://www.bauermedia.com/pdf/studien/zielgruppe/frauen/Der_Markt_der_Unterhaltenden_Frauenzeitschriften.pdf Der Markt der Unterhaltungszeitschriften]{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} {{de icon}}</ref> During the second quarter of 2016 its circulation was 236,427 copies.<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131001628/http://www.mediaimpact.de/en/artikel/Advertising-rates-Magazines-Advertising-rates-Magazines-2016_24609292.html|title=Advertising rates Magazines 2016|url=https://www.mediaimpact.de/en/artikel/Advertising-rates-Magazines-Advertising-rates-Magazines-2016_24609292.html|work=Media Impact|accessdate=18 September 2016|archivedate=31 January 2016}}</ref>
