[[File:Red bana Jelacica.JPG|thumb|upright|Order of Ban Jelačić]]
The '''Order of Ban Jelačić''' ({{lang-hr|Red bana Jelačića}}) is the 9th most important medal given by the [[Republic of Croatia]]. The order was founded on April 1, 1995. The medal is awarded for excellence in the [[Armed Forces of the Republic of Croatia]].<ref>{{cite journal | url = http://www.nn.hr/clanci/sluzbeno/1995/0377.htm | journal = [[Narodne novine]] | issue = 1995/20 | author = [[Croatian Parliament]] | language = Croatian | title = Zakon o odlikovanjima i priznanjima Republike Hrvatske | date = 1995-03-24 | accessdate = 2011-11-16}}</ref> It is named after the [[ban of Croatia]] [[Josip Jelačić]].

